<plot>Gary and his dog Pal (Flame the Wonder Dog) are having fun working on make-believe crime cases, though Gary's father (John Ridgely), a city detective, disapproves. Gary and Pal soon find themselves involved in a real case involving fur thieves. (Flame, never a dog to get type-cast, also essayed the role of Rusty in the Columbia series by that name.)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420777</url></doc>
